				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thanks <img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":-)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> </p>
<p>Re the logical problem: I had thought that if air currents were strong enough, and there was the force of the arrow shot and the bird fell badly, that its neck could be broken and the fall would be violent before the stop. Couldn&#8217;t this possibility happen?</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/2010/08/22/the-fall/?replytocom=422#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "div-comment-422", "422", "respond", "212" )' aria-label='Reply to cbraz'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
